OL,6,FA man who was on holiday in Cornwall
OL,7,Fhas been jailed for sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting a teenager.
OL,10,FDarren Oldham, 35 and from
OL,11,FOxfordshire, attacked the victim
OL,12,Fshortly after meeting her and a friend
OL,13,Ffor the first time at a beach near
OL,14,FHayle.
OL,16,FOldham gave the girls alcohol and
OL,17,Fcannabis. Police say when he was alone
OL,18,Fwith the "heavily intoxicated" victim
OL,19,Fand he sexually assaulted her before
OL,20,Ffleeing the scene.
