OL,6,FThe offence was reported to police the
OL,7,Fnext day and Oldham was arrested hours
OL,8,Flater.
OL,10,FOldham, of Middleton Road in Banbury,
OL,11,Fwas also convicted of sexually
OL,12,Fassaulting a teenager in South
OL,13,FYorkshire in a separate attack.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,16,Fassault on a female.
OL,18,FOn Wednesday 7 February Oldham was
OL,19,Fsentenced to nine years in prison,
OL,20,Fwith an extended licence period of
OL,21,Fthree years, at Sheffield Crown Court.
